Quadkey
=======

Usage
----

```
iex> qk = Quadkey.from_geo(35.658182, 139.702043, 15)
"133002112303013"

iex> Quadkey.from_quadkey("133002112303013")
{35.66622234103478, 139.691162109375}

iex> Quadkey.parent(qk)
"13300211230301"

iex> Quadkey.children(qk)
["1330021123030130", "1330021123030131", "1330021123030132", "1330021123030133"]

iex> Quadkey.around(qk)
["133002112303010", "133002112303012", "133002112303030", "133002112303011",
 "133002112303031", "133002112303100", "133002112303102", "133002112303120"]
```
